WEBVTT


00:00:49.220 --> 00:00:52.950
[The Ferry Man: 10th Anniversary]

00:00:53.580 --> 00:00:56.060
[Episode 20]

00:01:14.430 --> 00:01:14.950
Xu.

00:01:16.930 --> 00:01:17.820
-Xu.
-Dad.

00:01:17.840 --> 00:01:18.770
Are you alright?

00:01:18.840 --> 00:01:19.640
The employee badge has fallen off.

00:01:19.640 --> 00:01:21.030
Dad, Dad.

00:01:21.150 --> 00:01:22.080
Are you alright?

00:01:22.400 --> 00:01:23.070
I'm free.

00:01:23.870 --> 00:01:24.590
Honey,

00:01:25.350 --> 00:01:26.070
Niuniu,

00:01:27.230 --> 00:01:28.230
we're free!

00:01:32.750 --> 00:01:33.200
Okay.

00:01:38.350 --> 00:01:39.000
Thank you.

00:01:41.710 --> 00:01:43.120
Now that your blood pact is broken,

00:01:43.120 --> 00:01:44.789
your boss will definitely know.

00:01:44.789 --> 00:01:47.120
He will definitely send someone
to hunt you down.

00:01:47.120 --> 00:01:48.250
What are your plans?

00:01:49.200 --> 00:01:49.840
I didn't expect things

00:01:49.840 --> 00:01:51.300
to be resolved so quickly.

00:01:51.950 --> 00:01:53.550
We're leaving immediately.

00:01:53.640 --> 00:01:54.770
It's different now.

00:01:54.950 --> 00:01:55.840
Most of my demonic power

00:01:55.840 --> 00:01:57.170
has returned to my body.

00:01:57.920 --> 00:01:59.320
I can use my demonic power

00:01:59.680 --> 00:02:00.400
to conceal my demonic aura

00:02:00.400 --> 00:02:01.600
and Niuniu's as well.

00:02:02.640 --> 00:02:03.900
We will leave this city

00:02:04.050 --> 00:02:05.230
and live in seclusion in a small place.

00:02:05.230 --> 00:02:06.280
He won't find us.

00:02:07.120 --> 00:02:08.030
Hurry up and go.

00:02:08.150 --> 00:02:08.960
Thanks a lot.

00:02:14.150 --> 00:02:15.000
Wait a minute.

00:02:19.750 --> 00:02:20.800
Didn't we agree on this?

00:02:20.800 --> 00:02:22.600
How did things turn out this way?

00:02:23.030 --> 00:02:25.710
Daddy and Mommy are fighting.

00:02:29.190 --> 00:02:30.050
You can hear it?

00:02:31.360 --> 00:02:32.680
What are you whispering about?

00:02:32.680 --> 00:02:34.540
Are you hiding something from us?

00:02:37.800 --> 00:02:38.520
I'm sorry.

00:02:40.590 --> 00:02:42.190
There are indeed some things

00:02:42.240 --> 00:02:43.150
we hid from you.

00:02:43.560 --> 00:02:45.000
We've been looking for over a year

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:46.470
for a way to remove the employee badge.

00:02:46.470 --> 00:02:48.430
I didn't expect it to go so smoothly.

00:02:48.430 --> 00:02:49.430
I didn't lie.

00:02:50.280 --> 00:02:51.960
I really do want to leave the company

00:02:51.960 --> 00:02:53.620
and live a good life with them.

00:02:54.000 --> 00:02:55.000
But Niuniu

00:02:55.590 --> 00:02:56.650
is the main reason.

00:02:57.520 --> 00:02:58.380
It's like this.

00:02:58.910 --> 00:03:00.170
The company has a rule.

00:03:00.710 --> 00:03:02.460
If demons give birth to children,

00:03:02.460 --> 00:03:03.290
they are forced to enter

00:03:03.290 --> 00:03:04.550
the company's system.

00:03:04.630 --> 00:03:06.560
In the basement of Blue Blood Tech,

00:03:07.430 --> 00:03:08.710
there is a so-called

00:03:09.360 --> 00:03:10.400
Children's Park.

00:03:11.910 --> 00:03:12.710
I understand.

00:03:13.360 --> 00:03:14.810
Following in their parents' footsteps,

00:03:14.810 --> 00:03:16.910
slaving away generation after generation.

00:03:16.910 --> 00:03:18.590
The rationale provided by the boss

00:03:18.590 --> 00:03:20.120
is that demons or children

00:03:20.280 --> 00:03:21.470
with demon blood

00:03:21.840 --> 00:03:23.240
can't survive in society

00:03:23.520 --> 00:03:25.250
and will bring bad influences.

00:03:25.280 --> 00:03:25.910
So,

00:03:26.360 --> 00:03:27.020
when the children

00:03:27.020 --> 00:03:28.350
are almost one year old,

00:03:28.520 --> 00:03:30.750
they are all required
to enter the Children's Park.

00:03:30.750 --> 00:03:32.840
No one has ever been
to the Children's Park.

00:03:32.840 --> 00:03:33.800
I've been worried about this

00:03:33.800 --> 00:03:35.190
since I got pregnant.

00:03:35.590 --> 00:03:36.430
After all, I worked at the company

00:03:36.430 --> 00:03:37.710
for a while.

00:03:38.470 --> 00:03:39.360
I managed

00:03:40.400 --> 00:03:42.200
to briefly hack into the system.

00:03:42.400 --> 00:03:43.310
It's inhumane.

00:03:43.800 --> 00:03:44.660
No matter what,

00:03:44.910 --> 00:03:45.710
I won't let Niuniu

00:03:45.710 --> 00:03:46.430
go in there.

00:03:47.120 --> 00:03:48.780
All the children are so young.

00:03:49.430 --> 00:03:50.520
They lay in beds

00:03:51.180 --> 00:03:52.640
with tubes in their heads,

00:03:53.560 --> 00:03:55.360
inserted right into their skulls.

00:03:55.360 --> 00:03:57.220
No matter when the children go in,

00:03:57.280 --> 00:03:58.400
they'll never grow up, right?

00:03:58.400 --> 00:03:58.840
Right.

00:03:59.470 --> 00:04:01.190
All the kids are at the same age,

00:04:01.190 --> 00:04:02.320
around one year old.

00:04:02.520 --> 00:04:03.240
I see.

00:04:04.000 --> 00:04:05.240
This employee badge,

00:04:06.150 --> 00:04:07.360
besides bearing the blood pact,

00:04:07.360 --> 00:04:08.520
has another function.

00:04:08.520 --> 00:04:09.190
What is it?

00:04:09.520 --> 00:04:11.120
To drain your demonic power.

00:04:12.630 --> 00:04:14.520
You mean those kids...

00:04:14.590 --> 00:04:15.840
Remember what Situ Fei

00:04:15.840 --> 00:04:16.680
said?

00:04:17.550 --> 00:04:18.839
To run such massive

00:04:18.870 --> 00:04:20.190
and complex algorithms,

00:04:20.190 --> 00:04:20.829
of course, it requires

00:04:20.829 --> 00:04:22.630
a tremendous amount of energy.

00:04:23.240 --> 00:04:25.390
It requires a massive amount of energy.

00:04:25.390 --> 00:04:26.950
Fusing the two worlds

00:04:27.070 --> 00:04:28.530
requires massive energy.

00:04:28.630 --> 00:04:29.510
This energy

00:04:29.680 --> 00:04:31.430
comes from the demonic power of demons.

00:04:31.430 --> 00:04:33.040
Those young children

00:04:33.120 --> 00:04:34.600
are constantly having
their demonic power drained.

00:04:34.600 --> 00:04:35.310
So

00:04:35.870 --> 00:04:36.750
they won't grow up?

00:04:36.750 --> 00:04:37.360
Yes.

00:04:37.680 --> 00:04:38.830
Lying there forever

00:04:38.830 --> 00:04:39.600
without aging or dying,

00:04:39.600 --> 00:04:40.510
until their demonic power

00:04:40.510 --> 00:04:41.840
is completely drained.

00:04:42.159 --> 00:04:43.360
Then they turn into

00:04:44.600 --> 00:04:45.750
lifeless mummies.

00:04:46.430 --> 00:04:47.750
Those beasts!

00:04:48.920 --> 00:04:49.800
Even one-year-old kids

00:04:49.800 --> 00:04:52.130
have to be drained of their demonic power!

00:04:52.480 --> 00:04:53.240
Don't be afraid.

00:04:53.240 --> 00:04:54.440
Come, let me hold you.

00:04:57.159 --> 00:04:57.870
Mr. Zhao,

00:04:58.159 --> 00:04:58.920
we both hope

00:04:59.159 --> 00:05:00.070
that it's not just Niuniu

00:05:00.070 --> 00:05:01.000
who can be saved.

00:05:01.310 --> 00:05:02.630
Those demons' children

00:05:02.630 --> 00:05:03.630
are innocent too.

00:05:04.040 --> 00:05:04.750
Please.

00:05:05.750 --> 00:05:06.510
You two

00:05:07.040 --> 00:05:08.570
want me to save all the kids?

00:05:09.180 --> 00:05:09.920
This is what you are

00:05:09.920 --> 00:05:10.780
supposed to do.

00:05:11.240 --> 00:05:12.480
Situ Fei

00:05:12.510 --> 00:05:13.600
is a heinous demon.

00:05:14.160 --> 00:05:15.290
As a night watchman,

00:05:15.360 --> 00:05:17.040
you should step in and save them.

00:05:17.040 --> 00:05:17.750
Go away.

00:05:18.020 --> 00:05:19.040
I am a night watchman.

00:05:19.040 --> 00:05:20.400
I'm not God.

00:05:23.310 --> 00:05:25.440
Are you going to save these kids or not?

00:05:26.010 --> 00:05:27.000
The night watchmen,

00:05:27.000 --> 00:05:28.310
empowered by the righteousness
of heaven and earth,

00:05:28.310 --> 00:05:31.680
are dedicated to eliminating evil
and demonic deeds in the world.

00:05:31.680 --> 00:05:33.360
Turn it off. Turn it off.

00:05:33.360 --> 00:05:34.390
I'll save them, okay?

00:05:34.390 --> 00:05:35.520
That's more like it.

00:05:35.630 --> 00:05:36.830
Xu can help too.

00:05:37.000 --> 00:05:37.630
Right.

00:05:39.000 --> 00:05:40.510
But attacking Blue Blood Tech

00:05:40.510 --> 00:05:41.570
won't be that easy.

00:05:42.070 --> 00:05:42.600
Underground,

00:05:42.600 --> 00:05:44.200
there are many demon guards.

00:05:44.720 --> 00:05:46.510
We don't need to attack the building.

00:05:46.510 --> 00:05:47.800
For a system operated by demonic power,

00:05:47.800 --> 00:05:49.360
we just need to kill Situ Fei,

00:05:49.360 --> 00:05:50.680
and if he loses his demonic power,

00:05:50.680 --> 00:05:52.240
the whole system will collapse.

00:05:52.240 --> 00:05:52.680
But

00:05:53.159 --> 00:05:54.690
no one knows where he lives.

00:05:55.020 --> 00:05:56.650
No one has even seen him leave

00:05:56.680 --> 00:05:57.920
the Blue Blood Tech building.

00:05:57.920 --> 00:05:58.510
And...

00:05:59.560 --> 00:06:00.190
he...

00:06:00.490 --> 00:06:01.690
he can appear anytime

00:06:01.720 --> 00:06:02.720
right behind you.

00:06:03.430 --> 00:06:04.560
I remember this morning

00:06:04.560 --> 00:06:06.090
when you were fighting him,

00:06:07.950 --> 00:06:09.460
we seemed to have entered

00:06:09.510 --> 00:06:11.190
another virtual cyberspace.

00:06:11.800 --> 00:06:12.560
What do you mean?

00:06:12.560 --> 00:06:14.020
He should be living there.

00:06:14.270 --> 00:06:15.270
In another world?

00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:18.720
How about we go

00:06:18.720 --> 00:06:20.830
to Blue Blood Tech tomorrow to catch him?

00:06:20.830 --> 00:06:21.750
Tomorrow,

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:23.360
Situ Fei will find out

00:06:23.560 --> 00:06:24.750
that the blood pact has been destroyed

00:06:24.750 --> 00:06:25.920
and Xu has escaped.

00:06:26.430 --> 00:06:27.490
Why would he see us?

00:06:28.160 --> 00:06:28.750
You two,

00:06:28.950 --> 00:06:29.800
if you want to enter

00:06:29.800 --> 00:06:30.750
the cyber world,

00:06:31.510 --> 00:06:32.470
I can help.

00:06:45.560 --> 00:06:46.800
My daily job

00:06:47.040 --> 00:06:48.980
is to convert demonic power into code.

00:06:48.980 --> 00:06:50.010
I can extract

00:06:50.159 --> 00:06:51.159
your consciousness.

00:06:51.159 --> 00:06:51.800
But...

00:06:53.000 --> 00:06:54.730
I can't access the core system.

00:06:54.890 --> 00:06:55.770
I can try to see

00:06:55.800 --> 00:06:56.930
if I can hack into it.

00:06:57.190 --> 00:06:57.750
Come on.

00:07:09.430 --> 00:07:10.560
Do I have to go in too?

00:07:11.160 --> 00:07:13.000
What are you saying?

00:07:13.090 --> 00:07:14.160
"Do I have to go in too?"

00:07:14.160 --> 00:07:14.890
You let me...

00:07:14.950 --> 00:07:15.390
Fine.

00:07:15.920 --> 00:07:16.720
If you're afraid of dying,

00:07:16.720 --> 00:07:17.520
I can go alone.

00:07:17.800 --> 00:07:19.130
I'm not afraid of dying.

00:07:19.270 --> 00:07:20.510
I just feel that right now,

00:07:20.510 --> 00:07:21.390
I have no skills.

00:07:21.390 --> 00:07:23.050
I'm afraid I'll drag you down.

00:07:25.510 --> 00:07:26.110
Take this.

00:07:27.000 --> 00:07:27.800
Why are you giving me this?

00:07:27.800 --> 00:07:28.600
Your weapon.

00:07:30.190 --> 00:07:31.070
All worlds

00:07:31.310 --> 00:07:32.510
are made of thoughts.

00:07:32.800 --> 00:07:33.950
The world we're going to

00:07:33.950 --> 00:07:35.480
is not a real physical environment.

00:07:35.480 --> 00:07:37.140
Maybe just like Situ Fei said,

00:07:37.430 --> 00:07:38.690
with a single thought,

00:07:38.830 --> 00:07:39.960
it becomes reality.

00:07:40.600 --> 00:07:42.659
What do you mean? I don't understand.

00:07:42.720 --> 00:07:43.580
I've hacked in.

00:07:45.240 --> 00:07:45.750
You two,

00:07:47.159 --> 00:07:47.960
are you ready?

00:07:51.040 --> 00:07:51.640
Let's try.

00:07:51.920 --> 00:07:52.310
Okay.

00:07:56.630 --> 00:07:57.560
I'm sorry, guys.

00:07:58.450 --> 00:07:59.450
I will extract

00:07:59.480 --> 00:08:00.310
your consciousness.

00:08:00.310 --> 00:08:01.240
But I can't follow you

00:08:01.240 --> 00:08:02.170
into the system.

00:08:02.680 --> 00:08:03.430
However, I will stay here

00:08:03.430 --> 00:08:04.630
and guard your bodies.

00:08:04.630 --> 00:08:05.800
So please make sure

00:08:06.120 --> 00:08:07.250
to come back safely.

00:08:15.040 --> 00:08:15.750
Hurry up!

00:08:16.720 --> 00:08:17.190
Done.

00:08:22.430 --> 00:08:23.230
Zhao Hengzhi?

00:08:25.910 --> 00:08:26.830
Where are you?

00:08:31.510 --> 00:08:32.309
Zhao Hengzhi?

00:08:36.840 --> 00:08:37.640
Zhao Hengzhi.

00:08:38.630 --> 00:08:39.600
Where are we?

00:08:40.630 --> 00:08:41.890
There is no sound here.

00:08:42.030 --> 00:08:42.669
No wind.

00:08:43.240 --> 00:08:44.120
Nothing at all.

00:08:44.630 --> 00:08:45.270
Here,

00:08:47.000 --> 00:08:48.860
it is emptiness and nothingness.

00:08:49.910 --> 00:08:50.630
Then we...

00:08:51.240 --> 00:08:52.240
Keep your voice down.

00:08:52.240 --> 00:08:53.500
Don't let him hear you.

00:08:54.010 --> 00:08:55.000
Where are we going to find

00:08:55.000 --> 00:08:55.750
Situ Fei?

00:08:58.870 --> 00:08:59.870
With a thought,

00:09:01.150 --> 00:09:02.210
let there be light.

00:09:05.960 --> 00:09:07.160
What you said is true.

00:09:07.550 --> 00:09:08.870
With a thought...

00:09:09.320 --> 00:09:10.390
It can conjure up

00:09:12.440 --> 00:09:13.550
myriad worlds.

00:09:15.670 --> 00:09:17.070
The sun is too scorching.

00:09:17.760 --> 00:09:18.910
My skin is not great to begin with.

00:09:18.910 --> 00:09:20.570
It can't take any more damage.

00:09:20.720 --> 00:09:21.600
I want...

00:09:23.000 --> 00:09:25.150
an umbrella.

00:09:30.800 --> 00:09:32.180
Why can't I do it?

00:09:32.430 --> 00:09:33.830
You are not pious enough.

00:09:33.910 --> 00:09:35.170
Not confident enough.

00:09:45.120 --> 00:09:46.720
There's still nothing here.

00:09:50.240 --> 00:09:51.240
What are you doing?

00:09:51.240 --> 00:09:51.960
Here

00:09:53.080 --> 00:09:54.200
is a door.

00:10:00.270 --> 00:10:01.930
-What's behind?
-Don't move.

00:10:04.440 --> 00:10:05.120
Behind this

00:10:07.390 --> 00:10:09.200
is Situ Fei's room.

00:10:14.720 --> 00:10:15.480
Push it open.

00:10:30.910 --> 00:10:31.970
What is that sound?

00:10:38.200 --> 00:10:39.460
The sound of seawater.

00:10:40.030 --> 00:10:40.960
This is...

00:10:45.960 --> 00:10:46.750
Situ Fei

00:10:47.440 --> 00:10:48.790
is a demon of the sea.

00:10:49.200 --> 00:10:49.960
This is the bottom of the sea.

00:10:49.960 --> 00:10:51.160
Don't say it out loud.

00:10:52.240 --> 00:10:54.120
This is an illusory cyberspace.

00:10:54.450 --> 00:10:55.670
Except for Situ Fei's consciousness

00:10:55.670 --> 00:10:56.600
existing here,

00:10:57.000 --> 00:10:58.320
there is nothing else.

00:11:11.950 --> 00:11:13.000
He's sleeping.

00:11:13.600 --> 00:11:14.600
Don't wake him up.

00:11:17.440 --> 00:11:19.300
Why isn't he snoring in his sleep?

00:11:30.360 --> 00:11:31.890
I want to turn you into a gun.

00:11:51.870 --> 00:11:53.800
Plus the blood of a night watchman,

00:11:54.240 --> 00:11:55.550
all manner of evil spirits,

00:11:55.550 --> 00:11:56.550
and Samadhi Fire,

00:11:56.960 --> 00:11:58.690
strike true with a single blow.

00:12:03.240 --> 00:12:03.870
It's over.

00:12:08.200 --> 00:12:08.870
This...

00:12:09.720 --> 00:12:10.240
Oh no.

00:12:10.550 --> 00:12:11.240
He's a fake.

00:12:16.390 --> 00:12:17.050
Over there!

00:12:19.080 --> 00:12:20.010
Night Watchman.

00:12:21.390 --> 00:12:22.910
How did you break in here?

00:12:23.550 --> 00:12:24.200
Situ Fei.

00:12:24.680 --> 00:12:26.360
We know all your dirty dealings

00:12:26.360 --> 00:12:27.160
at Blue Blood.

00:12:27.200 --> 00:12:28.400
Your system operates

00:12:28.440 --> 00:12:30.030
by exploiting the demonic power of demons!

00:12:30.030 --> 00:12:31.160
We know everything!

00:12:32.960 --> 00:12:34.120
So what?

00:12:37.910 --> 00:12:39.040
The night watchmen,

00:12:39.360 --> 00:12:41.240
empowered by the righteousness
of heaven and earth,

00:12:41.240 --> 00:12:43.340
are dedicated to eliminating evil
and demonic deeds in the world!

00:12:43.340 --> 00:12:45.000
I will enforce justice
on behalf of heaven!

00:12:45.000 --> 00:12:46.390
Enforce justice on behalf of heaven?

00:12:46.390 --> 00:12:47.360
You're standing

00:12:47.360 --> 00:12:48.750
in my world.

00:12:48.900 --> 00:12:51.180
I am the only god in this world.

00:12:51.390 --> 00:12:53.390
I am the only way in this world!

00:12:54.150 --> 00:12:54.750
Why?

00:12:55.240 --> 00:12:57.150
Do you dare to kill a god?

00:12:57.420 --> 00:12:58.210
You are just

00:12:58.240 --> 00:13:00.300
a demon who has committed many evils!

00:13:01.630 --> 00:13:04.000
Go to hell!

00:13:14.320 --> 00:13:15.530
All manner of evil spirits
burn the evil to ashes!

00:13:15.530 --> 00:13:15.960
Burn!

00:13:24.150 --> 00:13:25.840
This is actually the bottom of the sea.

00:13:25.840 --> 00:13:26.500
You forgot.

00:13:26.790 --> 00:13:28.000
Your fire can't ignite

00:13:28.000 --> 00:13:29.000
within my domain.

00:14:01.910 --> 00:14:02.840
Do you guys feel like

00:14:02.840 --> 00:14:04.040
it's hard to breathe?

00:14:18.120 --> 00:14:18.720
Dongqing!

00:14:19.080 --> 00:14:20.740
Dongqing, don't believe him!

00:14:21.030 --> 00:14:22.830
This is an illusory cyberspace!

00:14:23.080 --> 00:14:24.390
There is nothing here!

00:14:56.030 --> 00:14:57.320
I'm getting serious.

00:15:01.600 --> 00:15:02.550
Zhao Hengzhi,

00:15:03.010 --> 00:15:04.550
don't think just because you
changed clothes,

00:15:04.550 --> 00:15:06.000
you can do anything to me.

00:15:11.630 --> 00:15:14.320
With infinite heaven and earth,
borrow the power of the universe!

00:15:14.320 --> 00:15:15.790
Samadhi Fire, burn!

00:15:50.440 --> 00:15:51.080
Dongqing!

00:15:51.400 --> 00:15:52.730
Target at his real body!

00:16:24.200 --> 00:16:26.060
What have you done to me?

00:16:27.360 --> 00:16:28.440
You've ruined me.

00:16:30.480 --> 00:16:31.750
And you've ruined...

00:16:33.600 --> 00:16:34.630
this world.

00:16:44.630 --> 00:16:45.510
We did it.

00:16:51.270 --> 00:16:52.120
Zhao Li's gun.

00:16:53.120 --> 00:16:53.840
It hit him.

00:16:54.790 --> 00:16:55.990
He's turned to ashes.

00:17:01.480 --> 00:17:03.210
This space has been destroyed.

00:17:04.000 --> 00:17:05.069
No, wait.

00:17:06.160 --> 00:17:07.310
How do we get out of here now?